stanford.androidlib

Class SimpleNotification

  • java.lang.Object
    • NotificationCompat.Builder
      • stanford.androidlib.SimpleNotification

  • public class SimpleNotification
extends NotificationCompat.Builder
    This class is a drop-in replacement for Notification.Builder that adds a few methods for convenience. Notably you can call .send(id); to build and send the notification without having to explicitly grab the NotificationManager service.

    This class is not currently well documented. It will be documented fully in a future release.
